        <underline method="pen" type="straight" language="LA" text="Vestros denique honores, quos eramus gradatim singulos assecuti"/>
        <underline method="pen" type="straight" language="LA" text="eam complecti oratione"/>
        <underline method="pen" type="straight" language="LA" text="Qu&ograve;d si ipsius summa dignitas, macim&aacute;eque res gestae non satis valerent: tamen filii pietas, propinquorum preces, adolesce[n]tium squallor, 
